During 2FA SMS verification, you will receive one-time passcodes (OTP) via SMS to verify your identity during login and account-related security processes.
You can cancel the SMS service at any time. Just text “STOP” to the short code. After you text “STOP,” we will send you a confirmation message, after which you will no longer receive SMS messages from us. If you’d like to rejoin, simply opt in again, and messaging will resume.
