You must post a set of "Official Rules" for your Promotion that includes all disclosures required by all applicable laws, rules and regulations, including:
A statement, as applicable, that "no purchase is necessary to enter or win."
A statement that the promotion is "void where prohibited."
Who is eligible to enter, including age and geographic eligibility restrictions.
A description of how to enter.
A description of the prize(s) and their approximate market value(s).
How winner(s) will be selected and an odds statement (e.g., "odds of winning depend on the number of entries received").
