canceling of any or all of Buyer's pending Transactions (both as Buyer or Seller) on the App;
withholding of any payments due to Buyer in its capacity as Buyer or Seller for up to thirty (30) days or until the violation has been remedied;
placing limits on Buyer's ability to buy and/or sell Items;
charging Buyer, via the Payment Method or otherwise, or setting-off with claims owed to Buyer for costs, expenses, and fees incurred by Whatnot as a result of Buyer's intentional or negligent failure to properly comply with these Terms; and
temporarily or permanently suspending Buyer's Account.
